Show each employee's name, department, salary, and the name of the highest-paid employee in their department.

Solution:

SELECT
CONCAT(first_name, " ", last_name) AS full_name,
department,
salary,
FIRST_VALUE(CONCAT(first_name, " ", last_name)) OVER(PARTITION BY department ORDER BY salary DESC) AS highes_paid_employee_per_department
FROM employees
